Invocation Name: math counts countdown
des:
Practice 160 total mathcounts questions fro both the chapter and state levels to keep you math skill sharp!

Alexa will be your moderator, question reader, and score keeper, so you only need to focus on answering the questions!

If your Alexa device is screen enabled, then you could also read the questions on the screen.

The questions are provided by the mathcounts website.
